{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AudioDestinationNode","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode\"><code>AudioDestinationNode</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode/maxChannelCount\"><code>maxChannelCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p><code>AudioDestinationNode 은 주어진 컨택스트의 음원의 종착점을 나타냅니다. 보통 스피커를 가리킵니다. 이는 또한 </code><code>OfflineAudioContext를 사용해 데이터가 녹음되는 노드가 되기도 합니다.</code></p>\n<code>AudioDestinationNode</code> has no output (as it <em>is</em> the output, no more <code>AudioNode</code> can be linked after it in the audio graph) and one input.&nbsp; 입력받은 음원의 채널의 총 갯수는 반드시 0과 <code>maxChannelCount값의 사이에 있거나 예외(an exception is raised)가 발생한다.</code>\n\n<p>주어진 <code>AudioContext의 </code><code>AudioDestinationNode는 </code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BaseAudioContext/destination\"><code>AudioContext.destination</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>프로퍼티를 통해 검색이 된다.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Number of inputs</th>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Number of outputs</th>\n   <td><code>0</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Channel count mode</th>\n   <td><code>\"explicit\"</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Channel count</th>\n   <td><code>2</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Channel interpretation</th>\n   <td><code>\"speakers\"</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Inherits properties from its parent, </em><em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"audiodestinationnode.maxchannelcount_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode/maxChannelCount\"><code>AudioDestinationNode.maxChannelCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>unsigned long 형의 물리적인 디바이스로 다룰수 있는 최대 채널의 갯수.</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>No specific method; inherits methods from its parent, </em><em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></em>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>AudioDestinationNode를 사용하면 복잡한 세팅없이 몇줄의 코드로 오디오 그래프를 확인할 수 있습니다.</code></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> audioCtx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AudioContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> source <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> audioCtx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createMediaElementSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myMediaElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nsource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gainNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ngainNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>audioCtx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>destination<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>To see a more complete implementation, check out one of our MDN Web Audio examples, such as <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/voice-change-o-matic/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Voice-change-o-matic</a> or <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/violent-theremin/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Violent Theremin</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webaudio/#the-audiodestinationnode-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Audio API<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'AudioDestinationNode' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.AudioDestinationNode","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Using_Web_Audio_API\">Using the Web Audio API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"AudioDestinationNode 은 주어진 컨택스트의 음원의 종착점을 나타냅니다. 보통 스피커를 가리킵니다. 이는 또한 OfflineAudioContext를 사용해 데이터가 녹음되는 노드가 되기도 합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AudioDestinationNode","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"AudioDestinationNode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AudioDestinationNode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"AudioDestinationNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/audiodestinationnode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/audiodestinationnode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode","title":"AudioDestinationNode"}],"pageTitle":"AudioDestinationNode - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}